task.summary: App is now translated in both Italian and English. Translations are now possible.
New Cart, fixed building, added stuff. Bugfixes.
CeliEye now has a new logo and a brand new site! (Still W.I.P)!
Added new graphics. Still need to be polished, though.

Introduced Motion Perspective Design Element. Upgrade will be gradual, but can be already experienced with XHDPI and upwards devices (Nexus 7 II, etc.). Also introduced the Tiling Element in the Settings layout. This update will be gradual as usual but it's already effecting XHDPI and up devices.
Brand new graphics for all resolutions.
Brand new graphics for all resolutions.
First time activity added. for use in branch -release and -preview2 Also removed useless xml from AndroidManifest
Added Splash Screen, optimised FTA Code & introduced Search Component.
Removed Data from Main View. This revision also includes the new FTA and Splash Screen, alongside the Search Functionality.
Finished FTA, database now gets deleted from SDCard
Read/Write a File for Cart function
Reworked UI paradigms for Tablets and adjusted UI elements for phones
